### Trigger a test transaction
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "amount": 12,
  "category": "food",
  "merchant": "Starbucks KLCC",
  "description": "Iced latte"
}

###

### Approve autosave
POST http://localhost:3000/autosave/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "amount": 8,
  "nudgeId": "nudge-abc123"
}

###

### Get transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/user123

